# Python Command Runner

- Run Python project commands through `uv run` so they use the repo environment.
- Prefer `uv run pytest ...` over bare `pytest`.
- Prefer `uv run python ...` over bare `python` when running scripts or modules.
- If a command fails because a tool is missing globally, retry it through `uv run` before changing code.
